            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9ee8",
          "text": "Along with John Seed, Joanna Macy and Pat Fleming, Arne Naess is regarded as the originator of the deep ecology movement. The conceptual and perceptual expansion of the self beyond the skin boundary and to experience and understand ourselves as a relational self, or “ecological self” is a central theme in deep ecology.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 20,
              "href": "http://www.rainforestinfo.org.au/deep-eco/jsbio.htm",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 11,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
