          "name": "6ec0",
          "text": "Arne Næss was a Norwegian philosopher who inspired the Deep Ecology movement; other key people who have promoted deep ecology work around the world include Joanna Macy & Chris Johnstone, and Stephan Harding (image left, image middle, image right)",
