            }
          ],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_13",
          "href": null,
          "name": "546c",
          "text": "The wellbeing and flourishing of human and nonhuman life on Earth have value in themselves (synonyms: inherent worth; intrinsic value; inherent value). These values are independent of the usefulness of the nonhuman world for human purposes.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5246",
          "text": "Richness and diversity of life forms contribute to the realization of these values and are also values in themselves.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "203a",
          "text": "Humans have no right to reduce this richness and diversity except to satisfy vital needs.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "018c",
          "text": "Present human interference with the nonhuman world is excessive, and the situation is rapidly worsening.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "555f",
          "text": "The flourishing of human life and cultures is compatible with a substantial decrease of the human population. The flourishing of nonhuman life requires such a decrease.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "62ac",
          "text": "Policies must therefore be changed. The changes in policies affect basic economic, technological, and ideological structures. The resulting state of affairs will be deeply different from the present.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a7b5",
          "text": "The ideological change is mainly that of appreciating life quality (dwelling in situations of inherent worth) rather than adhering to an increasingly higher standard of living. There will be a profound awareness of the difference between big and great.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "cd9e",
          "text": "Those who subscribe to the foregoing points have an obligation directly or indirectly to participate in the attempt to implement the necessary changes.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "61940b2373f3_21",
          "href": null,
          "name": "cf60",
          "text": "",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
